{"tid":218073,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"觸 動 人 心 的 片 刻","createTime":"2017-04-26T08:54:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T14:17:10.000Z","uid":93127,"like":90,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"63bbad8dd3555895001731c66111122f4126292c","tid":218073,"uid":93127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:54:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oPd7xY5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoPd7xY5.jpg&h=5a3adec6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一位婦人為了孩子 為了居住 以一己之力抵抗隊伍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/77tpV1k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F77tpV1k.jpg&h=3800c7d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女孩沒有溫飽 緊抱著死去了的老鼠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/thOe7RD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FthOe7RD.jpg&h=eaa5afe8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另一種的一步一生 伴男孩不同成長階段的義肢"},{"pid":"7b71bbc34ab2ad448378b3c2f4d1669a39be8a0a","tid":218073,"uid":93127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:55:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7SHYW8g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7SHYW8g.jpg&h=0e7675e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n四兄妹在玩 姐姐在旁親吻最上面的妹妹<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9AyXePn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9AyXePn.jpg&h=cb46fccd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同理心 比勝利贏得更多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8041p4p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8041p4p.jpg&h=1d471f04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以天橋底作學堂 兩名老師義務教育貧窮的孩子"},{"pid":"006264a667bebba303e3041af4837e6ed4a4c2fb","tid":218073,"uid":93127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:56:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/421M59C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F421M59C.jpg&h=b9ebf36b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n椅子還在 但是老人的妻子已經去世了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JX2v965.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJX2v965.jpg&h=7fdc0036&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n母猴子為了想逃脫 帶著孩子走著危險的邊界<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/97x5dSi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F97x5dSi.jpg&h=0d389626&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n孩子想看得更高 看得更遠 － 父親來支持你"},{"pid":"26a71b56247fc1dacceac7bfe7771a52c7ce04f5","tid":218073,"uid":93127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:56:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k57U0oH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk57U0oH.jpg&h=f404e5d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n比賽回來 男子下輪椅並單膝跪地 她感動得想哭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d6m47V7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd6m47V7.jpg&h=4d7228b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n合力將小男孩送出戰爭區 才能讓他活下去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/10es974.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F10es974.jpg&h=6c1e8ab1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一位攝影師把自己的鞋子贈給這個沒鞋穿的女子"},{"pid":"c21d064c929fcdd466869cd808f4e923138d07ed","tid":218073,"uid":93127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:57:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W5pEf26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW5pEf26.jpg&h=11e77979&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n戰事過來回來 美國士兵抱著自己的女兒大哭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eb443Zs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Feb443Zs.jpg&h=fa946bcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不管是誰 甚麼身份 這刻的快樂是真摰的<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8bT46un.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8bT46un.jpg&h=1ee81ece&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n發生了水災 屋主小心翼翼安頓他的寵物"},{"pid":"d80ee7943a0ed1f4f6e6e477e1b1057186c599d5","tid":218073,"uid":93127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XiaM319.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXiaM319.jpg&h=46ad60b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小孩在父親的紀念碑前舉手敬禮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nRkt8bR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnRkt8bR.jpg&h=72a79a69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n獸醫完成了手術 愛犬看到他就撲向他 累得靠在他胸前睡了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/182V636.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F182V636.jpg&h=67f7c436&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n某場殘奧會中一名美國選手用腳拉弓的一刻"},{"pid":"7ec1c175726281ddde0dc98402cc9fe957293af2","tid":218073,"uid":93127,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T09:01:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/44yP9nW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F44yP9nW.jpg&h=befd9794&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n著名的一張照片 流浪漢跟愛犬不離不棄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/64zGo62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F64zGo62.jpg&h=4a4beb3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n士兵跟他們的伴侶吻別<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WV3KB5F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWV3KB5F.jpg&h=39d2de1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拯救隊照料著一隻樹熊 給了牠喝水<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所有圖片經過重新搜尋 盡量最佳畫質<br />\n<br />\nvia<br />\n<a href=\"http://tw.aboluowang.com/2017/0423/917840.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.aboluowang.com%2F2017%2F0423%2F917840.html&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=efa460bf\" target=\"_blank\">http://tw.aboluowang.com/2017/0423/917840.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://beauties.life/?p=168148\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbeauties.life%2F%3Fp%3D168148&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=36331856\" target=\"_blank\">http://beauties.life/?p=168148</a>"},{"pid":"57f24e28c6934f2c8